127
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:45,583
{\an8}(CHICKEN CLUCKS)

128
00:06:47,458 --> 00:06:49,083
{\an8}They say hens are good luck.

129
00:06:49,166 --> 00:06:52,791
{\an8}Yeah, I don't know. Because it's not
in the Chinese horoscope.

130
00:06:52,875 --> 00:06:54,375
{\an8}(BOTH CHUCKLE)

131
00:06:58,916 --> 00:07:02,791
{\an8}I think I can wait three hours
