149
00:08:45,666 --> 00:08:47,958
{\an8}TOKYO: <i>I brought that bottle</i>
<i>to drink with Rio.</i>

150
00:08:48,750 --> 00:08:52,500
{\an8}<i>♪ A den will have to be created ♪</i>

151
00:08:53,208 --> 00:08:56,250
{\an8}TOKYO: <i>As I danced,</i>
