152
00:08:56,333 --> 00:08:59,208
{\an8}<i>Those who break up</i>
<i>and feel the need to wish you the best.</i>

153
00:08:59,791 --> 00:09:02,458
{\an8}<i>Like, "Take care, be happy."</i>

154
00:09:03,208 --> 00:09:07,708
{\an8}<i>♪ Everyone who takes their measurements ♪</i>

155
00:09:08,541 --> 00:09:09,875
TOKYO:<i> Rio is one of them.</i>

156
00:09:11,666 --> 00:09:15,083
{\an8}<i>And then there's people like me,</i>
<i>who can be a fucking bitch about it.</i>

157
00:09:19,375 --> 00:09:20,875
(TOKYO CHUCKLES)

158
00:09:21,791 --> 00:09:24,166
Excuse me. Should I wait outside?

159
00:09:24,250 --> 00:09:26,500
No, there's nothing
you haven't seen before.

160
00:09:27,166 --> 00:09:29,166
(MUSIC FADES IN HEADPHONES)

161
00:09:31,250 --> 00:09:33,291
Rio, I wanted to tell you…

162
00:09:35,041 --> 00:09:37,166
You did what we should have done
a long time ago.

163
00:09:37,250 --> 00:09:39,541
Hey. Not a long time ago.

164
00:09:40,125 --> 00:09:41,333
We had fun together.

165
00:09:42,250 --> 00:09:44,250
Even though I'm sure
you're pissed right now,

166
00:09:44,333 --> 00:09:45,875
you haven't beat the shit out of me yet.

167
00:09:45,958 --> 00:09:47,041
(CHUCKLES)

168
00:09:48,333 --> 00:09:49,583
Yeah, we had our fun.

169
00:09:52,916 --> 00:09:54,416
We had good moments.

170
00:09:55,958 --> 00:09:58,125
But that wasn't enough.

171
00:10:02,708 --> 00:10:04,291
We got wrapped up in all this.

172
00:10:05,291 --> 00:10:08,166
Wrapped up in what?
What the fuck are you talking about?

173
00:10:09,541 --> 00:10:11,833
The heist. The pressure.

174
00:10:12,583 --> 00:10:14,208
(TOILET FLUSHES)

175
00:10:15,208 --> 00:10:17,125
Being millionaires.

176
00:10:19,875 --> 00:10:20,708
Hello, Denver.

177
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:26,375
- I didn't hear anything.
- Hmm? (CHUCKLES)

178
00:10:28,458 --> 00:10:30,583
- DENVER: See you later.
- Where are you going?

179
00:10:30,666 --> 00:10:32,583
- TOKYO: Don't go, don't go.
- What?

180
00:10:32,666 --> 00:10:35,458
Rio, did you know
I almost hooked up with Denver?

181
00:10:35,541 --> 00:10:37,458
